<p><strong>1. What is the Winx Club about?</strong></p>
<p>The Winx Club story revolves around six young fairies who attend Alfea College for Fairies. Led by the determined Bloom, they discover their magical powers and embark on thrilling adventures to protect the magical dimension from evil forces. Along the way, they forge unbreakable bonds, confront personal challenges, and learn valuable life lessons.</p>
