<p><strong>3. What are the main characters in the Winx Club story?</strong></p>
<p>The six Winx fairies are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Bloom: The leader of the group, known for her Dragon Flame power</li>
<li>Stella: The fashion-loving princess of Solaria</li>
<li>Flora: The nature-loving fairy with plant-controlling abilities</li>
<li>Musa: The musical fairy and aspiring musician</li>
<li>Tecna: The intelligent and tech-savvy fairy</li>
<li>Aisha: The strong and athletic fairy with water-based powers</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>4. What are the key themes of the Winx Club story?</strong></p>
<p>The Winx Club story explores themes of friendship, courage, self-discovery, and the importance of believing in oneself. It empowers young viewers to embrace their unique abilities and strive for their dreams, while also highlighting the value of teamwork and perseverance.</p>
